@NODE "Main" "Install Random Backgrounds"

                      
                      Random Backgrounds Script
                          for PerfectPaint

                 © Copyright 2001 Georges Halvadjian
                    All Rights Reserved, FreeWare




@{bg shine} Intro @{bg back}

  This script allows you to start PerfectPaint with random Backgrounds
  for Desktop and Requester


@{bg shine} Install @{bg back}

  - Copy 'RdBackgrounds.rx' to 'PerfectPaint:Rexx/General/'

  - Start PerfectPaint

  - On the StartUp requester @{" Image " link "RdBackgrounds.iff/Main" 0}
           - Enable 'StartupScript'
           - Select 'PerfectPaint:Rexx/General/RdBackgrounds.rx'

  - Enter PerfectPaint:
      If you install the script for the first time, PerfectPaint 
      will open a requester. It allows you to select the path
      for Backgrounds Requester and for Backgrounds Desktop.


